<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
spell [spell_name] : eg, "spell create food", or "spell ogre strength"<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
This command will give you background information on the particular spell<br>
you are looking up.  Information in the file should include energy cost,<br>
number of turns to cast, a brief description on the effects, and a listing<br>
of any reagents needed to complete the spell.<br>
<br>
To see a listing of the spells available to any class, look in help<br>
abilities.  Other useful help files pertaining to magic include leech and<br>
magic.<br>
</html>
</body>
